      • SYNC_DECISIONS_REQUEST

        public static final PaxosPacket.PaxosPacketType SYNC_DECISIONS_REQUEST
        Request to retrieve missing decisions. A replica sends out this request when it has received a decision with slot number n+K but not n for a sufficiently large K. The value of K is generally a constant fixed at initialization time to a value based on the expected, normal length of the outstanding request pipeline. However, a paxos instance additionally tries to sync more aggressively at creation time, i.e., the effective K is small, e.g., 1, because it is more likely that different instances got created at different times and some instances missed some decisions but the gap is much smaller than the default K.
